            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/75658bb2db7e736e/text/000000198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-75658bb2db7e736e-f09fcd twpub-75658bb2db7e736e-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">Section 4.  Information about Donations to the Project Gutenberg\nLiterary Archive Foundation</h4></div>"
