            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/75658bb2db7e736e/text/000000202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-75658bb2db7e736e-f09fcd twpub-75658bb2db7e736e-6b4cd0\"><p>International donations are gratefully accepted, but we cannot make\nany statements concerning tax treatment of donations received from\noutside the United States.  U.S. laws alone swamp our small staff.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/75658bb2db7e736e/text/000000203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/75658bb2db7e736e/text/000000203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-75658bb2db7e736e-f09fcd twpub-75658bb2db7e736e-6b4cd0\"><p>Please check the Project Gutenberg Web pages for current donation\nmethods and addresses.  Donations are accepted in a number of other\nways including checks, online payments and credit card donations.\nTo donate, please visit: http://pglaf.org/donate</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/75658bb2db7e736e/text/000000204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/75658bb2db7e736e/text/000000204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-75658bb2db7e736e-f09fcd twpub-75658bb2db7e736e-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">Section 5.  General Information About Project Gutenberg-tm electronic\nworks.</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/75658bb2db7e736e/text/000000205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/75658bb2db7e736e/text/000000205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-75658bb2db7e736e-f09fcd twpub-75658bb2db7e736e-6b4cd0\"><p>Professor Michael S. Hart is the originator of the Project Gutenberg-tm\nconcept of a library of electronic works that could be freely shared\nwith anyone.  For thirty years, he produced and distributed Project\nGutenberg-tm eBooks with only a loose network of volunteer support.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/75658bb2db7e736e/text/000000206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/75658bb2db7e736e/text/000000206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-75658bb2db7e736e-f09fcd twpub-75658bb2db7e736e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">Project Gutenberg-tm eBooks are often created from several printed\neditions, all of which are confirmed as Public Domain in the U.S.\nunless a copyright notice is included.  Thus, we do not necessarily\nkeep eBooks in compliance with any particular paper edition.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/75658bb2db7e736e/text/000000207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/75658bb2db7e736e/text/000000207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-75658bb2db7e736e-f09fcd twpub-75658bb2db7e736e-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">Most people start at our Web site which has the main PG search facility:</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/75658bb2db7e736e/text/000000208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/75658bb2db7e736e/text/000000208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-75658bb2db7e736e-f09fcd twpub-75658bb2db7e736e-6b4cd0\"><p>     http://www.gutenberg.org<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/75658bb2db7e736e/text/000000209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/75658bb2db7e736e/text/000000209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-75658bb2db7e736e-f09fcd twpub-75658bb2db7e736e-6b4cd0\"><p>This Web site includes information about Project Gutenberg-tm,\nincluding how to make donations to the Project Gutenberg Literary\nArchive Foundation, how to help produce our new eBooks, and how to\nsubscribe to our email newsletter to hear about new eBooks.</p></div>"
        },
